object.script:
delay = property.getNumber("Launch delay")
function onTick() battery = input.getNumber(6) temperature = input.getNumber(7) fuel = input.getNumber(8)
launch = input.getBool(1) buzzer = input.getBool(8)
end
function onDraw() screen.setColor (0,200,0) width = screen.getWidth() height = screen.getHeight()
if not buzzer and not launch then delay = property.getNumber("Launch delay") screen.drawTextBox(0,8,width,5,"HOLD",0,0) screen.drawTextBox(0,16,width,5,"W",0,0) elseif buzzer then delay = delay - 1/60 screen.drawTextBox(0,8,width,5,"LAUNCH",0,0) screen.drawTextBox(0,16,width,5,string.format("%.1f",delay),0,0) else screen.drawText(1,5,"BAT") if battery < 0.3 then screen.setColor (200,0,0) end screen.drawTextBox(17,5,15,5,string.format("%.1f",battery),0,0) screen.setColor (0,200,0)
screen.drawText(1,13,"FUL") if fuel < 20 then screen.setColor (200,0,0) end screen.drawTextBox(17,13,15,5,math.floor(fuel),0,0) screen.setColor (0,200,0)
screen.drawText(1,21,"TMP") if temperature > 100 then screen.setColor (200,0,0) end screen.drawTextBox(17,21,15,5,math.floor(temperature),0,0) screen.setColor (0,200,0)
end
end

function onTick() heading = math.fmod((360-input.getNumber(9)*360),360) speed = input.getNumber(1) altitude = input.getNumber(2) pitch = input.getNumber(3)
launch = input.getBool(1) buzzer = input.getBool(8)
speedTrue = 3.6*speed/math.cos(math.pi*2*pitch) end
function onDraw() width = screen.getWidth() height = screen.getHeight() screen.setColor (0,200,0)
if not buzzer and not launch then screen.drawTextBox(0,8,width,5,"HOLD",0,0) screen.drawTextBox(0,16,width,5,"W",0,0) elseif buzzer then screen.drawTextBox(0,8,width,5,"HOLD",0,0) screen.drawTextBox(0,16,width,5,"W",0,0) else
for step = 0,35,5 do offset = math.fmod(heading, 15)/3 screen.drawLine(step+offset, 0, step+offset, 2) end for step = 0,45,15 do offset = math.fmod(heading, 45)/3 screen.drawLine(step+offset, 0, step+offset, 3) end
screen.drawTextBox(1,4,width,7,math.floor(heading), 0, 0) screen.drawText(1,13,"SPD") screen.drawTextBox(17,13,15,5,math.floor(speedTrue),0,0) screen.drawText(1,21,"ALT") screen.drawTextBox(17,21,15,5,math.floor(altitude),0,0) end end

delay = property.getNumber("Launch delay")
function onTick() gpsX = input.getNumber(10) gpsY = input.getNumber(11)
launch = input.getBool(1) buzzer = input.getBool(8)
end
function onDraw() screen.setColor (0,200,0) width = screen.getWidth() height = screen.getHeight() screen.setMapColorOcean(10, 10, 10) screen.setMapColorShallows(20, 20, 20) screen.setMapColorLand(30, 30, 30) screen.setMapColorGrass(30, 30, 30) screen.setMapColorSand(30, 30, 30) screen.setMapColorSnow(30, 30, 30)
if not buzzer and not launch then delay = property.getNumber("Launch delay") screen.drawTextBox(0,8,width,5,"HOLD",0,0) screen.drawTextBox(0,16,width,5,"W",0,0) elseif buzzer then delay = delay - 1/60 screen.drawTextBox(0,8,width,5,"LAUNCH",0,0) screen.drawTextBox(0,16,width,5,string.format("%.1f",delay),0,0) else screen.drawMap(gpsX,gpsY,property.getNumber("Map zoom")) screen.drawCircle(width/2,height/2,1) end
end

freqLow = 500 freqHigh = 600
maxDelay = 7 delay = maxDelay
RFreq = freqLow TFreq = freqLow
first = true firstFirst = true
callsign = string.sub(string.upper(property.getText("Callsign")), 1, 8)
function onTick()
if first then if firstFirst then firstFirst = false output.setNumber(14, TFreq)
for i = 1, #callsign do output.setNumber(i + 4, string.byte(callsign, i)) end
elseif delay <= 0 then
if input.getBool(1) then TFreq = TFreq + 1 output.setNumber(14, TFreq) delay = maxDelay else first = false output.setNumber(13, TFreq) end
end delay = delay - 1 else
output.setNumber(1, input.getNumber(10)) --gpsX output.setNumber(2, input.getNumber(11)) --gpsY output.setNumber(3, input.getNumber(2)) --altitude output.setNumber(4, input.getNumber(1)) --seed
output.setBool(1, true)
RFreq = RFreq + 1 if RFreq > freqHigh then RFreq = freqLow end
output.setNumber(14, RFreq)
correctFreq = RFreq - 5 if correctFreq < freqLow then correctFreq = correctFreq + (freqHigh - freqLow) + 1 end
if input.getBool(1) and correctFreq == TFreq then
first = true firstFirst = true
delay = maxDelay
TFreq = freqLow + 10 + math.floor(gpsX % 10) end end end
